title: Picnic Time's Piccadilly 202-19
transcripts: The Piccadilly basket by Picnic time is reminiscent of times when picnics were grand affairs and life's pace afford you the time to enjoy them to the fullest. This traditional red and white plaid willow basket measures 16 inches long and has an easy access double lid design with service for two it includes two 8 inch melamine plates, two eight-ounce PS wine glasses, two stainless steel forks, knives, and spoons with plastic handles misting the steel way to style corkscrew. It also features a matching role up flatware pouch premium leather accents and a woven will handle plan to take the Piccadilly on your next outing and enjoy life's finer moments.
